The product arrived in great shape and in a timely manner. The cartoon itself is really not that great. Pretty cheesy.
I purchased this for my nephew for Christmas.  He is a huge Zelda fan  and this was a hit with him.  While it is an older show, if your a true Zelda fan, I think you will like this!

Loved the Zelda Nintendo games but this series makes Link out to be a hormonal adolescent. A reward is a kiss or some favor by Zelda for protecting her. Pretty sexist in my opinion. I was expecting more game like thinking in a TV series and solving issues and puzzles.
Made for a great gift! Received very well!
I thought it was a movie, its just a couple of episodes, the description isn't at all clear of what is on the disk.
Beware when you order this item. My son really wanted to see this show after his daddy told him about it. I ordered the 2-pack as a gift and they sent me only one DVD.
